# Local Development Guardrails

## 🚀 Branch & Merge Management
- **Pre-Merge Manual Testing Guardrail:** 
  Before merging any feature branch into the `main` branch, the agent MUST stop and prompt the user to perform manual testing on the active branch. 
  - **Constraint:** Never execute `git push` or `gh pr merge` / merge commits directly without explicit user instruction and validation of the working environment.
